

<h1>QR Code Generator</h1>
A simple and responsive QR Code Generator built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This tool allows users to input any text or URL, which is converted into a QR code using an external API. The generated QR code is displayed dynamically on the page with a smooth transition effect.
<br>
<hr>
Features<br>
Instant QR Code Generation: Input any text or URL, and a QR code will be generated immediately.<br>
Responsive Design: The layout is responsive and adapts to different screen sizes.<br>
User-Friendly Interface: A clean, minimalistic UI makes the tool easy to use.<br>
Smooth Animation: The QR code container smoothly expands when a code is generated.<br>
API Integration: Uses the QRServer API to generate QR codes.<br>
Technologies Used<br>
HTML: For structuring the content.<br>
CSS: For styling the interface and adding smooth transitions.<br>
JavaScript: For handling user input and generating the QR code dynamically.<br>
